OL,3,C'It felt inhumane' - Mum with full-
OL,4,Ctime job threatened with eviction twice
OL,6,FA mother from Solihull who works full-
OL,7,Ftime said she fears she and her
OL,8,Fchildren could end up homeless after
OL,9,Fbeing threatened with eviction for the
OL,10,Fsecond time.
OL,12,FAngela Carruthers, 36, is one of
OL,13,Faround 12,500 families in the West
OL,14,FMidlands facing the same struggle,
OL,15,Funable to keep up with rising rents
OL,16,Fand the soaring cost of living.
OL,18,FTwo years ago, Angela and her three
OL,19,Fchildren were evicted from their
OL,20,Fprivate rented home of 12 years.
