OL,3,C'It felt inhumane' - Mum with full-
OL,4,Ctime job threatened with eviction twice
OL,6,FSince then, they have been moved from
OL,7,Fplace to place, three times in total
OL,8,Fand the single mother now sleeps on a
OL,9,Fbed in the living room.
OL,11,F"It's not the best, I'd rather the
OL,12,Fkids have their own bedrooms, but I
OL,13,Fdon't get any privacy at all," Angela
OL,14,Ftold ITV News Central.
OL,16,F"The neighbours opposite can see
OL,17,Fstraight into the living room, so it's
OL,18,Fnot ideal.
OL,20,F"This is half bedroom, half living
OL,21,Froom, but it doesn't look good.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
