OL,3,C'It felt inhumane' - Mum with full-
OL,4,Ctime job threatened with eviction twice
OL,6,FAnd the stress did not stop there.
OL,7,FAngela was threatened with eviction
OL,8,Fagain because, despite working full-
OL,9,Ftime, she could not keep up with
OL,10,Fhousing costs.
OL,12,FIt was only after contacting Shelter
OL,13,Fthat she got the support she needed to
OL,14,Fstay in the property.
OL,16,FAngela continued: "We were in our home
OL,17,Ffor over 12 years, and it was perfect.
OL,18,FThe kids loved it, their school and my
OL,19,Fwork was down the road, everything
OL,20,Fjust worked.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
