OL,3,C'It felt inhumane' - Mum with full-
OL,4,Ctime job threatened with eviction twice
OL,6,F"Then the landlord sold up and we were
OL,7,Fevicted. I couldn't get a viewing
OL,8,Fanywhere, the private rents were
OL,9,Fimpossible.
OL,11,F"That's when we ended up in temporary
OL,12,Faccommodation. It was freezing; no
OL,13,Fboiler, no heating, no hot water, we
OL,14,Fwere washing with kettle water out of
OL,15,Fa bowl.
OL,17,F"It felt inhumane. I'm working full-
OL,18,Ftime but still can't cover the rent.
OL,19,FI've had to borrow money just to feed
OL,20,Fmy kids.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
