OL,3,C'It felt inhumane' - Mum with full-
OL,4,Ctime job threatened with eviction twice
OL,6,FShe said: "It's utterly disgraceful
OL,7,Fthat across the country, more and more
OL,8,Ffamilies are being pushed to the brink
OL,9,Fof homelessness. Soaring rents, low
OL,10,Fincomes, and a chronic shortage of
OL,11,Fsocial homes mean that even parents
OL,12,Fwho work tirelessly to put food on the
OL,13,Ftable are struggling to keep a roof
OL,14,Fover their heads.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
