OL,3,C'It felt inhumane' - Mum with full-
OL,4,Ctime job threatened with eviction twice
OL,6,F"On this occasion, the accommodation
OL,7,Fthat was secured for Ms Carruthers was
OL,8,Fout of the area due to there being no
OL,9,Favailability within Solihull.
OL,11,F"We are sorry that the temporary
OL,12,Faccommodation offered was not up to
OL,13,Fthe required standard and the length
OL,14,Fof time taken to remedy the issues.
OL,15,FThis was not in keeping with our usual
OL,16,Fservice standards and in recognition
OL,17,Fof this we apologised and compensated
OL,18,FMs Carruthers for the distress and
OL,19,Finconvenience caused."
