OL,6,FSpeaking about the eviction threat,
OL,7,Fthey said: "Our Money Advice Team
OL,8,Fprovided details to Ms Carruthers
OL,9,Fabout what the cost of the temporary
OL,10,Faccommodation would be. We attempted
OL,11,Fto contact Ms Carruthers several times
OL,12,Fin respect of the rent and council tax
OL,13,Farrears but received no response.
OL,15,F"Now that we are in contact with Ms
OL,16,FCarruthers, we are working to help her
OL,17,Fclear the arrears and secure suitable
OL,18,Faccommodation either in the private
OL,19,Frented sector or an offer of social
OL,20,Fhousing."
